description: OMango is bringing Chicago fresh Indian food on the go! Cubside curry in a hurry without a worry (less than 500 calories) so taste and transcend. Come experience pure Indian cuisine - the traditional alongside the modern, distinctive flavors from bold to subtle, and the liveliness and vibrancy of the people.Smile and say paneer. These food and flavors are second to naan. Live a little, taste a lot!
name: OMango
